Package: gdstheme
Title: Xaringan Template With Government Digital Services Theme
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Matt",
           family = "Dray",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mwdray@gmail.com")
Description: A template and CSS files for reproducing the presentation style of
    Government Digital Services (GDS), part of the UK Government's Cabinet
    Office. GDS's templates are available internally as Google Slides only. This
    package lets you achieve that style but also use the power of RMarkdown.
